text: Josu Mirena Andueza Zabaleta (born 5 June 1973) is a Spanish rower. He competed in the men's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Spain Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Errenteria Category:Sportspeople from Gipuzkoa
